	bool "antlr3, 3.2 branch"
	select PACKAGE_BUILD_TOOLS_JAVA_STRINGTEMPLATE
	select PACKAGE_BUILD_TOOLS_JAVA_LIBANTLR
	help
	  ANTLR stands for (AN)other (T)ool for (L)anguage (R)ecognition and
	  generates LL(*) recursive-descent parsers. ANTLR is a language tool
	  that provides a framework for constructing recognizers, compilers, and
	  translators from grammatical descriptions containing actions.
